creator: Daraz Mobile
descriptionHtml:
The all new Shop Seller Center App for Android is now even more convenient than before! You can easily monitor your business almost anytime and anywhere. The App has a number of great features and you can now respond to growing customer demands at Shop quicker and with more ease. This new app allows you to sell online with comfort and ease. 📱🛒


Features:




1. Keep a track


The new Shop Seller Center App for Android makes it easier for you to view your Pending Orders. You quickly RTS them, and also keep a track of all your orders without missing any of them. 📈


2. Easy Update


With the new Shop Seller Center App for Android, you can update the stock count and even the pricing for your SKUs on Shop. 📲


3. Direct Publishing


You can now easily edit your products or product description and even publish products directly from the new Shop Seller App for Android. 📝


4. Be a part of Campaigns


With just a single tap, you can take part in upcoming campaigns and sales exclusively at Shop. 🎉


5. Be Responsive


The all new Shop Seller Center App allows you stay responsive. This way you can make the customers satisfied and reply to their messages and queries on the go. 📩


6. View your performance


You can easily view your Seller Dashboard with the all new Shop Seller Center App for Android. This will help you keep a track of your performance. 📊


So, worry no more! Simply download the new Shop Seller Center App now on your Android devices and stay connected to your Shop. Happy selling on Shop!

The all new Shop Seller Center App for Android is now even more convenient than before! You can easily monitor your business almost anytime and anywhere. The App has a number of great features and you can now respond to growing customer demands at Shop quicker and with more ease. This new app allows you to sell online with comfort and ease. 📱🛒


Features:




1. Keep a track


The new Shop Seller Center App for Android makes it easier for you to view your Pending Orders. You quickly RTS them, and also keep a track of all your orders without missing any of them. 📈


2. Easy Update


With the new Shop Seller Center App for Android, you can update the stock count and even the pricing for your SKUs on Shop. 📲


3. Direct Publishing


You can now easily edit your products or product description and even publish products directly from the new Shop Seller App for Android. 📝


4. Be a part of Campaigns


With just a single tap, you can take part in upcoming campaigns and sales exclusively at Shop. 🎉


5. Be Responsive


The all new Shop Seller Center App allows you stay responsive. This way you can make the customers satisfied and reply to their messages and queries on the go. 📩


6. View your performance


You can easily view your Seller Dashboard with the all new Shop Seller Center App for Android. This will help you keep a track of your performance. 📊


So, worry no more! Simply download the new Shop Seller Center App now on your Android devices and stay connected to your Shop. Happy selling on Shop!
